See C<--phase>.

=item B<--author-arg>=I<s>*

(No description)


Can also be specified as the 1st command-line argument.

=item B<--author-isnt>=I<s@>

(No description)


Can be specified multiple times.

=item B<--author>=I<s@>

(No description)


Can be specified multiple times.

