=over

=item B<--release>=I<s>*

(No description)


Can also be specified as the 1st command-line argument.

=back

=head2 Options for subcommand extract-script

=over

=item B<--all>, B<-a>

(No description)


=item B<--script>=I<s>*

(No description)


Can also be specified as the 1st command-line argument.

=back

